erve borders the iSimangaliso/Greater St. Lucia Wetland Park in the Maputaland region in northern KwaZulu-Natal.Africa Dream SafarisSpecializing in customized private safaris to East Africa, Africa Dream Safaris is accredited in the U.S. and Tanzania with memberships in the Tanzania Association of Tour Operators, Tanzania Tourist Board and the American Society of Travel Agents. View a variety of wildlife, schedule a traditional safari in the Serengeti or consider a balloon safari, cultural tour or a walking safari. If you want to add on to your safari, try one of the extension trips, including mountain gorilla or chimpanzee trekking or a visit to Ndarakwai Ranch in Kilimanjaro. Africa Dream Safaris Headquarters 4825 Torrance Blvd.Thanda Private Game ReserveAn experienced guide will lead your safari adventure to view the Big Five by open Land Rover. Guests can also participate in bush walks, game drives and wildlife lectures as well as trips to iSimangaliso to enjoy whale watching, horseback riding on the beach or diving and snorkeling excursions. The facilities include a luxurious main lodge, safari-style tented camp and an award-winning wellness center. It is the only private game reserve that's a member of The Leading Hotels of the World. It's close to the Indian Ocean, the heart of the Elephant Coast in northern KwaZulu-Natal.Email received from Standard Way ConsultingVisit here (http://getitnow.rsteamy.top/q/15677923) to end African Safari.Ads.Upper Pembroke Street 28-32, Dublin, D02 EK84standardwayconsulting.info/?/Historiography/f8f706c3938feec43d1f111ad3c0a047 | 2016 -=====================================-